      "content": "but my doctor said i need to keep it consistent so its not swinging up and down. if i wait all the way until tomorrow morning that's like 18 hours without anything in my system. wouldn't taking two now just help bring it back to where it's supposed to be faster? it feels safer than just leaving it blank",
