      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, you said taking two doses would lead to high blood pressure?? i thought lisinopril was for lowering it so more would just lower it more? isnt the whole point of the medication to keep the levels steady in my blood? if i skip a whole day the concentration drops way too low. i just want to know for sure if taking the extra one now is actually dangerous or if you're just being overly cautious",
